Rating: 2
Don't make this unless you have the ingredients on hand (such as leftover tomato sauce and cooked fish) -- otherwise it is a lot of effort and expense for an unspec tacular dish. I did put some of the leftover fish mixture in crepes as suggested below and thought it was nice.

