Rating: 3
This dish was excellent, but a ton of work! I added grated nutmeg to the bechamel, used savory crepes instead of no boil lasagne, and sauted the red pepper and swiss chard in garlic and olive oil. Overall delicious, but do not attempt this dish unless you have a lot of time for preparation.